title: BRIEF-Cashbuild Says HY ‍Headline Earnings Per Share Down 8 Pct​

* ‍HY DILUTED HEADLINE EARNINGS PER SHARE 1 097.4 CENTS VERSUS 1 188.5 CENTS YEAR AGO​
* ‍DECLARED INTERIM DIVIDEND OF 496 CENTS * ‍MANAGEMENT BELIEVE TRADING CONDITIONS WILL REMAIN EXTREMELY CHALLENGING​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
